comment.text: Binds 16S rRNA, required for the assembly of 30S particles and may also be responsible for determining the conformation of the 16S rRNA at the A site.

Part of the 30S ribosomal subunit (PubMed:10094780, PubMed:12809609, PubMed:16272117, PubMed:27934701, PubMed:12244297, PubMed:27906160, PubMed:27906161). Contacts proteins S3 and S10 (By similarity).
Belongs to the universal ribosomal protein uS14 family.
